# Financial Risk Market Interest Rate Shock Impact On EVBB Including Earnings Offset Amount

## identifier
de8120

## type
float

## definition
This is the change in the economic value of the banking book (EVBB), as at the relevant date, given a shock to interest rates, taking into account the earnings offset. 

This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.InterestRateShockImpactOnEVBBIncludingEarningsOffset.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
